' description: archive_plan 5 entity 并行 state 联动 — plan / worktree / branch / marker / sessions
' last_updated: 2026-05-29
@startuml archive-plan-state-machine

title archive_plan — 5 entity 并行 state 联动 (4 子模块原子收口: precheck + ff-merge + archive-fs + cleanup)

' 内部 module 名 / 函数名 / REVIEW 引用见 INDEX 第 3 列

' ─── entity 1: plan frontmatter ───
state "Plan frontmatter\n(plan 文件)" as PlanState {
  state "in_progress" as InProgress
  state "completed" as Completed
  state "abandoned (手工)" as Abandoned

  [*] --> InProgress
  InProgress --> Completed : archive-fs Step 9 改 frontmatter\n(+ final_commit + completed_at)
  InProgress --> Abandoned : 手工 §中止 (不入 git 归档)
  Completed --> [*]
  Abandoned --> [*]
}

' ─── entity 2: worktree 目录 ───
state "Worktree 目录" as WorktreeState {
  state "exists" as WorktreeExists
  state "removed" as WorktreeRemoved

  [*] --> WorktreeExists : enter_worktree 创建
  WorktreeExists --> WorktreeRemoved : cleanup Step 14 git worktree remove
  WorktreeRemoved --> [*]
}

' ─── entity 3: git branch ───
state "Git branch" as BranchState {
  state "exists" as BranchExists
  state "merged to base_branch" as BranchMerged
  state "deleted" as BranchDeleted

  [*] --> BranchExists : enter_worktree -b
  BranchExists --> BranchMerged : ff-merge Step 7-8c
  BranchMerged --> BranchDeleted : cleanup Step 14 branch -D
  BranchDeleted --> [*]
}

' ─── entity 4: cwdReleaseMarker ───
state "cwdReleaseMarker" as MarkerState {
  state "null" as MarkerNull
  state "set = <worktreePath>" as MarkerSet

  [*] --> MarkerNull
  MarkerNull --> MarkerSet : enter_worktree (plan-driven)
  MarkerSet --> MarkerNull : cleanup Step 13 清 marker (commit 后提前清)
}

' ─── entity 5: caller + teammate sessions ───
state "Caller + teammate sessions" as SessionState {
  state "caller active + teammate active/dormant" as SessionsActive
  state "teammate closed + caller active" as TeammateClosed
  state "全部归档" as AllArchived

  [*] --> SessionsActive
  SessionsActive --> TeammateClosed : runBatonCleanup phase 1
  TeammateClosed --> AllArchived : runBatonCleanup phase 2
  AllArchived --> [*]
}

' ─── 跨 entity 联动 + 失败兜底 ───

note as N1
  archive_plan **4 子模块原子收口**(facade 串联 precheck → ff-merge → archive-fs → cleanup; 每阶段 error 短路):
  ① Plan: InProgress → Completed (archive-fs Step 9)
  ② Worktree: exists → removed (cleanup Step 14)
  ③ Branch: exists → merged → deleted (ff-merge Step 7-8c + cleanup Step 14)
  ④ Marker: set → null (cleanup Step 13 提前到 commit 后)
  ⑤ Sessions: active → teammate closed → 全部归档 (phase 1+2)

  失败兜底 (双段语义):
  - **precheck / ff-merge 前失败 → 可 retry**: 4 entity 全停未变 + sessions 不动,caller fix 后重 invoke
  - **post-ff-merge 失败 (archive-fs / cleanup) → manual recovery 无自动 rollback**:
    · impl-archive-fs.ts:117-124 明文 "Cannot retry archive_plan as a whole"
    · impl-ff-merge.ts:93-108 / impl-cleanup.ts:230-247 走 postFfMergeErr 给手工 5 步 cleanup hint
    · archive-fs 阶段失败 (mv plan / INDEX update / commit) → ff-merge 已成功不可逆,caller 走手工 mv+commit
    · cleanup Step 13 clear marker 失败 → archive 已成功但 marker 可能残留;
      warnings 提示 caller 用 exit_worktree / session close 手工清理
      (stale marker 指向已不存在 worktree → 后续 archive_plan precheck 8 分支会 reject)
    · cleanup Step 14 worktree remove / branch -D 失败 → marker 已清 + worktree/branch 由 caller 手工 cleanup
  - phase 1 单 teammate close 失败 → 仅该 teammate warn,其他继续
  - phase 2 archive caller 失败 → archived='failed' warn-only,caller 仍 active

  与 hand_off baton 对比: archive_plan 不 spawn 新 session,
  4 子模块 (precheck/ff-merge/archive-fs/cleanup) + phase 1+2 = plan/worktree/team 整片收口
end note

@enduml
